OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FBoris Johnson: Welsh       
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25FSecretary Simon Hart quits 
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fcabinet                    
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Welsh Secretary Simon Hart has become  
OL,6, the latest cabinet member to resign    
OL,7, from Boris Johnson's government as     
OL,8, pressure continues to mount on the     
OL,9, prime minister.                        
OL,11,FHe was among senior cabinet ministers  
OL,12,Fwho earlier urged Mr Johnson to go.    
OL,14,FIn his resignation letter, Mr Hart said
OL,15,Fcolleagues had done their utmost to    
OL,16,F"turn the ship around" but he no longer
OL,17,Fthought it was possible.               
OL,19,FEarlier, Mr Johnson said he intended to
OL,20,F"keep going" in office.                
